<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - UBS RAISES BRODERBUND.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - UBS RAISES BRODERBUND.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-08-07</dateline>
<text>
<p>UBS Securities said analyst Michael Wallace upgraded Broderbund Software Inc to buy from hold.</p>
<p>-- said in a report that thinks the core education and productivity businesses have bottomed out.</p>
<p>-- said pricing appears to have stabilized, and competition is moving out of the market for the first time in a couple of years.</p>
<p>-- stock was up 1-3/8 to 23-1/4.</p>
</text>
